To compile:                         gcc globals.c select_pivots.c gsl_matrix.c index.c level.c cell.c file_buffer.c file_loader.c main.c -o ../bin/pexeso -lm -g -lgsl -lgslcblas
debug with valgrind:                valgrind  --undef-value-errors=no ../bin/pexeso
Binary conversion:                  little indian.
Base:
Number of bytes for integer:        4 (32 bits)
Number of bytes for floats:         4 (32 bits)
Number of bytes per binary file:    base * ((datasize * index->settings->num_pivots) + nsets) / 8